ed). Then `otherInput = c00`, and we'd do `doSwap(\"z05\", \"c00\")`, fixing the carry swap.\n\nSo the algorithm handles this correctly through the fallback logic. The problem I was seeing with the first test was a different issue. Let me verify the algorithm is robust by running build and lint."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":210,"cache_read_input_tokens":65698,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":210},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3f5d13e5-35da-470e-9db0-5db08f41ada9","uuid":"5e185fe7-7f9d-4232-9df9-bd86b8ad10f5"}
